										<div class="alert alert-warning">
											<p class="mb-0"><strong>Notice!</strong></p>
											<ul class="mb-1">
												<li>You will only see those project whose minimum budget is equal or
													greater than your entered values.</li>
												<li>Base currency is USD. For other currencies, budget will be converted
